reviewText: its cool to look learn some new moves.

It is only an instructional DVD, nothing romantically, or sexually notable about it. If anyone is looking for a Massage Instructional Video, I am sure there are many far more qualified than this one on the market.

The product itself gave good information for performing a relaxing and holistic massage. The use of the word "lesbian" in the title is somewhat misleading. There was nothing to suggest an intimate or even sexual relationship between the masseuse  and the recipient. Had you swapped out the masseuse for a male, it would have made no difference to the nature of what was being discussed as far as massage technique.
